This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not include the latest research findings. The complexity of climate systems means that while human activities are a significant factor, natural processes also play a role, which this report does not extensively cover. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may introduce biases or inaccuracies inherent in the original data.

